OL,3,CParalympian Stephen Miller 'emotional'
OL,4,Cas he signs off on sparkling career
OL,6,FSimon O'Rourke met Stephen Miller as
OL,7,Fhe reflected on his distinguished
OL,8,Fcareer in sport.
OL,10,FCramlington Para-athlete Stephen
OL,11,FMiller paid an emotional farewell to
OL,12,Fhis career in competitive sport as he
OL,13,Fmarked his retirement.
OL,15,FAn event was held at St James' Park in
OL,16,FNewcastle to celebrate his career,
OL,17,Fwhich spanned decades and saw him
OL,18,Fbecome one of Britain's most decorated
OL,19,FPara-athletes.
