OL,3,CParalympian Stephen Miller 'emotional'
OL,4,Cas he signs off on sparkling career
OL,6,FDuring his career, he has won 34 major
OL,7,Finternational medals - including
OL,8,FParalympic golds in Atlanta, Sydney
OL,9,Fand Athens.
OL,11,FAfter making his Paralympics debut in
OL,12,F1996, Miller went on to represent
OL,13,FGreat Britain at six consecutive
OL,14,Fgames, with his main event being the
OL,15,Fclub throw.
