OL,3,CParalympian Stephen Miller 'emotional'
OL,4,Cas he signs off on sparkling career
OL,6,FReflecting on his career, he said:
OL,7,F"It's like This Is Your Life. It's
OL,8,Fvery emotional, a bit surreal. To go
OL,9,Fback through my career was really
OL,10,Fgreat. I couldn't ask for a better end
OL,11,Fto my sports career.
OL,13,F"I'm retiring from sport, but not from
OL,14,Flife. So there's another challenge
OL,15,Faround the corner and I'll be
OL,16,Fapproaching it in exactly the same
OL,17,Fway."
