OL,4,Cas he signs off on sparkling career
OL,6,FAmong those sending messages of
OL,7,Fcongratulations to Stephen were
OL,8,FNewcastle United legend Alan Shearer
OL,9,Fand Geordie duo Ant and Dec.
OL,11,FProceeds from the event at St James'
OL,12,FPark went towards SMILE Through Sport,
OL,13,Fan organisation Stephen founded to
OL,14,Fpromote inclusivity and engagement by
OL,15,Fproviding opportunities for people
OL,16,Fwith disabilities to get involved in
OL,17,Fsport.
