OL,3,CParalympian Stephen Miller 'emotional'
OL,4,Cas he signs off on sparkling career
OL,6,FHe said: "I am very proud of how the
OL,7,FParalympics has developed and grown
OL,8,Fover the years, how the sport has
OL,9,Fbecome much more competitive. The
OL,10,Fperformance levels keep getting higher
OL,11,Fand higher every four years and that's
OL,12,Fdown to the dedication of the athletes.
OL,14,F"Hopefully I can support the charity
OL,15,Fto keep going and keep giving disabled
OL,16,Fpeople the opportunity to access sport
OL,17,Fin the North East."
